snippet.title: Bridge Constructor Studio | Announcement Trailer | Meta Quest Platform
snippet.description:
Bring your building techniques to new heights with Bridge Constructor Studio and unleash your engineering creativity in VR and MR. In virtual reality (Meta Quest 2 and 3) or mixed reality (Meta Quest 3 Only), you can build, try, walk around, and fix your bridge right in your living room.

Wishlist now, or make use of our 15% pre-order discount 💸 https://metaque.st/4gj3JTO
